  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/metalperformanceshadersgraph\/mpsgraphrnnactivation\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T20:17:54Z\n---\n\n# MPSGraphRNNActivation\n\n**Enumeration**\n\nThe activation modes for RNN operations.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nenum MPSGraphRNNActivation\n```\n\n## Enumeration Cases\n\n- **MPSGraphRNNActivation.hardSigmoid**: Defines a Hard sigmoid activation.\n- **MPSGraphRNNActivation.none**: Defines a pass through activation.\n- **MPSGraphRNNActivation.relu**: Defines a ReLU activation.\n- **MPSGraphRNNActivation.sigmoid**: Defines a Sigmoid activation.\n- **MPSGraphRNNActivation.tanh**: Defines a Tanh activation.\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
